data.description: Step into this remarkable ranch retreat in Chepachet, where contemporary updates seamlessly blend with enduring charm. Featuring a new roof and countertops on both the main and in-law sides, this home exudes elegance and functionality. Enjoy newly installed hardwood flooring adorned with recess lighting and abundant natural light throughout. With potential for in-law accommodations and separate entrances, versatility abounds. Ample parking, a basketball/tennis court, and two decks enhance outdoor living. Benefit from a new well monitoring system, 200-amp electrical, and updated appliances staying with the property. Situated in picturesque Chepachet, convenience meets tranquility. Schedule a private tour today and experience this distinguished property firsthand. (There is an annual $100 fee for the Keech Pond Association.)
